{
  "texts": [
    "We provide a quantitative study based on over 200K completions generated by the five models for over 7,000 events and two personas, spanning over 400 unique emotions.",
    "We find strong evidence that all models consistently exhibit gendered emotions.",
    "We then find that these variations are influenced by gender stereotypes.",
    "In addition, we perform a qualitative study that supports our findings.",
    "These findings align with psychology and gender studies of gender-based emotional stereotypes."
  ]
}